kms-cmake-utils (1.4.0) testing; urgency=medium

  [ Juan Navarro Moreno ]

  * Added:
    - New CMake module "DpkgBuildFlags", which allows to query the
      `dpkg-buildflags` command and retrieve the compilation flags that will be
      used to generate Debian packages. All projects now compile with these flags.
  * Changed:
    - Old ChangeLog.md moved to the new format in the CHANGELOG.md file.
    - Full review of all CMake files to tidy up and homogenize code style.
  * Prepare release 1.4.0

